        content: "O **hash table** (tabel de dispersie) este o structură de date care permite acces O(1) la elemente pe baza unei chei.\n\n**Conceptul fundamental:**\n```\nCheie (\"username\") → hash_function() → index → Valoare\n```\n\n**Hash function simplă:**\n```c\n#define TABLE_SIZE 100\n\nunsigned int hash(const char *key) {\n    unsigned int hash = 0;\n    while (*key) {\n        hash = hash * 31 + *key;\n        key++;\n    }\n    return hash % TABLE_SIZE;\n}\n```\n\n**Structura de baza:**\n```c\ntypedef struct {\n    char *key;\n    int value;\n    int occupied;  /* 0 = liber, 1 = ocupat */\n} HashEntry;\n\ntypedef struct {\n    HashEntry entries[TABLE_SIZE];\n    int count;\n} HashTable;\n\nvoid ht_init(HashTable *ht) {\n    memset(ht->entries, 0, sizeof(ht->entries));\n    ht->count = 0;\n}\n```\n\n**Complexitate:**\n- Insert: O(1) amortizat\n- Search: O(1) amortizat\n- Delete: O(1) amortizat\n- Worst case (coliziuni multe): O(n)"
